<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src ="/javascript/jquery.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src ="/javascript/timerLogic.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src ="/javascript/interface.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src ="/javascript/fiveLitreJug.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src ="/javascript/threeLitreJug.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src ="/javascript/waterPuzzle.js"></script>
    <meta charset="utf-8">

    <title>Die Hard Water Puzzle</title>

  </head>
  <body>

  <h1>Die Hard 3</h1>
  <h2>Water Puzzle</h2>

  <h6><span id="timer"></span></h6>

  <div class="status">
    <h3 id="threelitrestatus"></h3><h4 id="fivelitrestatus"></h4>
  </div>


  <div class="images">
    <img class="scales" src="https://i.imgur.com/YEGMEyG.png" alt="scales">
    <img class="smallbottle" src="https://i.imgur.com/x3al8hc.png" alt="smallbottle">
    <img class="largebottle" src="https://i.imgur.com/ks6dEyy.png" alt="largebottle">
  </div>

  <div class="buttons">
    <button class= "weigh" id="weigh" type="button">Weigh</button>
    <button class="fillthree" id="fillthree" type="button">Fill Three Litre Bottle</button>
    <button class="fillfive" id="fillfive" type="button">Fill Five Litre Bottle</button><br>
    <button class="reset" id="reset" type="button">Reset</button>
    <button class="emptythree" id="emptythree" type="button">Empty Three Litre Bottle</button>
    <button class="emptyfive" id="emptyfive" type="button">Empty Five Litre Bottle</button><br>
    <button class="instructions" id="instructions" type="button">Instructions</button>
    <button class="pourintofive" id="pourintofive" type="button">Pour Into Five Litre Bottle</button>
    <button class="pourintothree" id="pourintothree" type="button">Pour Into Three Litre Bottle</button>
  </div>

  <div id=winpopup class=winpopup style="text-align:center;">
    <h5>You Win!</h5>
    <p>You weigh the four litres of water and the bomb is defused!</p>
    <p>Refresh the page to play again.</p>
    <img class=smallimage src="https://i.imgur.com/SFw1srz.png" alt="well done">
  </div>

  <div id=losepopup class=losepopup style="text-align:center;">
    <h5>You Lose!</h5>
    <p>You ran out of time and the bomb went off. Oh no!</p>
    <p>Refresh the page to play again.</p>
    <img class=smallimage src="https://i.imgur.com/IH3L1oM.png" alt="boom">
  </div>

  <div id=helppopup class=helppopup style="text-align:center;">
    <h5>How To Play</h5>
    <p>Can you defuse the bomb?</p>
      <p>It will explode in five minutes unless a container with four litres of water inside is placed on the weighing scales.</p>
      <p>Use the buttons to fill, empty or transfer the contents of containers.</li>
      <p>The numbers above the containers show how many litres of water are currently inside them. You can empty both containers with the 'reset' button.</p>
      <p>To weigh the larger container and see if you defused the bomb, press the weigh button. You can fill, empty and transfer as much as you like- your only limit is time!</p>
    <button id="close" type="button">Close</button>
  </div>

  </body>

</html>
